{"tid":1368023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗件事等佢地狗咬狗，唔好再曬時間講","createTime":"2019-07-26T11:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T12:11:26.000Z","uid":33583,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a031e93924452f02c3575ecea501240ac8830e5d","tid":1368023,"uid":33583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:42:58.000Z","msg":"佢地唔妥大家係佢地既事<br />\n兩邊都係我地既敵人<br />\n就算佢地口講唔滿意<br />\n真係有事發生個時<br />\n佢地點都係同一陣線<br />\n所以依件事係佢地自己既事<br />\n我地唔需要曬時間理佢地<br />\n可能你地想藉依件事分化佢地<br />\n但係稍有不慎可能比對家攞著依點黎講<br />\n話政府已經重拾大眾既支持<br />\n咁我地就仆街<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再曬時間<br />\n諗下聽日點仲好過"},{"pid":"4c113bab9104fea6f9f768e2f763de96e36afc89","tid":1368023,"uid":33583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:47:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"839b46fffd31d22e073998f930785068a6613812","tid":1368023,"uid":33583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:47:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8563b2f9c850fb7c769cb57aed5e9269265b43a9","tid":1368023,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df0695a188c0f85ea14ee75da2e1dc0c21c5be7","tid":1368023,"uid":33583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:50:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c70ba90a994f62f9d9e40787ddcf81d5b768ec24","tid":1368023,"uid":33583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:50:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ff0710ba8f2d4b40ea4d4de3ff9d7d05d93a270","tid":1368023,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:51:02.000Z","msg":"可以利用 唔可以認同"},{"pid":"3771b8677d8fd156784c45945bc017b0d922d6d6","tid":1368023,"uid":114507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"花生不妨食吓，當正